---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Resume — Daniel Palmer"
  description="Daniel Palmer · Automation engineer turned AI analyst. CIS grad, ex-Fastenal RPA, now at Meraki Private Equity."
>
  <article class="resume mx-auto max-w-3xl">
    <div class="resume__toolbar flex items-center justify-between mb-8">
      <a
        href="/about"
        class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-(--color-text-dim) hover:text-(--color-accent-glow) transition-colors"
      >
        ← About
      </a>
      <a
        href="/daniel-palmer-resume.pdf"
        class="rounded-md border border-(--color-border) px-4 py-2 text-sm text-(--color-text-muted) transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-(--color-accent-glow) hover:text-(--color-text)"
        download
      >
        Download PDF
      </a>
    </div>

    <header class="resume__header">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.03em]">
        Daniel Palmer
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-2 text-(--color-text-muted)">
        Automation engineer turned AI analyst — Shoreview, MN
      </p>
      <ul class="resume__contact mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-1 text-sm text-(--color-text-muted)">
        <li>
          <a href="mailto:xdanielpalmerx@gmail.com" class="hover:text-(--color-accent-glow)">
            xdanielpalmerx@gmail.com
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://linkedin.com/in/dan-fpalmer"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="hover:text-(--color-accent-glow)"
          >
            linkedin.com/in/dan-fpalmer
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://danpalmer.dev"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="hover:text-(--color-accent-glow)"
          >
            danpalmer.dev
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </header>

    <section class="resume__section">
      <h2>Summary</h2>
      <p>
        Three years building rules-based RPA at Fastenal, now applying the
        same operational rigor to AI-augmented workflows at Meraki Private
        Equity. I focus on the boring part of automation: durable side
        effects, audit trails, and the long tail of edge cases.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="resume__section">
      <h2>Experience</h2>

      <article class="resume__role">
        <header class="resume__role-header">
          <h3>AI Analyst — Meraki Private Equity</h3>
          <span class="resume__role-meta">April 2026 – Present · Remote</span>
        </header>
        <p class="resume__role-blurb">
          Embedding Claude into Gradient Financial Group workflows. Owning
          design and rollout of AI-augmented analyst tooling.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="resume__role">
        <header class="resume__role-header">
          <h3>RPA Developer — Fastenal</h3>
          <span class="resume__role-meta">January 2023 – April 2026 · Winona, MN</span>
        </header>
        <ul class="resume__bullets">
          <li>
            Shipped 100+ production automations on a 7-person team — collectively
            saved $30M+ across the org.
          </li>
          <li>
            Built and owned the SAP Taulia UI automation that eliminated an 8-hour-per-week
            recurring task across ~20 customer accounts (~400 hours/year).
          </li>
          <li>
            Wrote and reviewed UiPath, Python, and C# workflow code. Pushed for
            durable logging and reproducible side effects across the team's library.
          </li>
          <li>
            Mentored two new hires through their first quarter of bot ownership.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="resume__section">
      <h2>Selected projects</h2>
      <ul class="resume__bullets">
        <li>
          <strong><a href="/work/sap-taulia-ui-automation">SAP Taulia UI Automation</a></strong>
          — production RPA at Fastenal; eliminated 400 hours/year of manual data pulls.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong><a href="https://studywheel.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Bible Study Wheel</a></strong>
          — public app with real users; React + TypeScript + Supabase + Tailwind v4.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="resume__section">
      <h2>Education</h2>
      <article class="resume__role">
        <header class="resume__role-header">
          <h3>B.S. Computer Information Systems — Winona State University</h3>
          <span class="resume__role-meta">Graduated December 2023</span>
        </header>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="resume__section">
      <h2>Skills</h2>
      <ul class="resume__skills">
        <li><strong>Automation:</strong> UiPath, Python automation, SAP scripting, web/UI automation</li>
        <li><strong>AI:</strong> Claude API, prompt design, agentic workflows, evaluation harnesses</li>
        <li><strong>Web:</strong> TypeScript, React, Astro, Tailwind, Supabase, Node</li>
        <li><strong>Discipline:</strong> reproducible side effects, audit logging, observability, code review</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Screen styling — uses the same tokens as the rest of the site. */
  .resume__section {
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }
  .resume__section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .resume__role + .resume__role {
    margin-top: 1.75rem;
  }
  .resume__role-header {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .resume__role-header h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  .resume__role-meta {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
  }
  .resume__role-blurb,
  .resume__section > p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .resume__bullets {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .resume__bullets li + li {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }
  .resume__bullets strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  .resume__skills {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .resume__skills li + li {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }
  .resume__skills strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
  }

  /* Print stylesheet — strip the chrome, force light contrast, keep type rhythm. */
  @media print {
    @page {
      margin: 0.6in;
    }
    :global(html),
    :global(body) {
      background: #ffffff !important;
      color: #111111 !important;
    }
    :global(header[role="banner"]),
    :global(nav[aria-label="Primary"]),
    :global(.bgfx),
    :global(footer),
    .resume__toolbar {
      display: none !important;
    }
    .resume {
      max-width: 100% !important;
      padding: 0 !important;
      margin: 0 !important;
    }
    .resume h1,
    .resume h2,
    .resume h3,
    .resume strong {
      color: #000 !important;
    }
    .resume__section h2 {
      color: #555 !important;
      border-bottom-color: #999 !important;
    }
    .resume__role-meta,
    .resume__contact,
    .resume__role-blurb,
    .resume__bullets,
    .resume__skills,
    .resume__section > p {
      color: #222 !important;
    }
    .resume a {
      color: #000 !important;
      text-decoration: none !important;
    }
  }
</style>
